	<description>	
	<![CDATA[
<p>JA University Template for Joomla 2.5</p>

<p>JA University will be the choice for your next school or university website project. The template is designed with the aim for simple and minimal design. JA University has various content types. This Joomla template for educational purpose supports the latest version of T3 Framework, K2 component, Slideshow Lite and much more.</p>

<p>JA University will meet all the demands of a professional educational website.</p>

<p><strong>Note:</strong> JA University does not support RTL language</p>
</br>

